Package: valama
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libguanako1 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Vala IDE
 Valama is the next generation Vala IDE.
 It comes with the guanako Vala autocompletion library and provides easy symbol
 lookups and supports cmake build system.

